ClevoLEDKeyboardControl
=======================

This project is a fork of ClevoRGBControl (https://github.com/xuha233/ClevoRGBControl),
which itself was inspired by moshuiD/Colorful-Keyborad-Led-Color-Setting
(https://github.com/moshuiD/Colorful-Keyborad-Led-Color-Setting).

