Modifications in this fork
--------------------------
In accordance with GPL-3.0 section 5(a), the following modifications have been
made to the original work:

- 2026-06-10: Forked from xuha233/ClevoRGBControl @ commit 90d2438
  ("Clean repository metadata"). Renamed product to "ClevoLEDKeyboardControl"
  across user-facing strings, installer paths, Windows service name, registry
  keys, scripts, release notes and update-check endpoints. Removed the bundled
  proprietary driver asset (assets/driver/InsydeDCHU.dll) from the repository
  and documented how end users obtain it from the OEM Control Center software.
  Legacy service names "ClevoRGBControlService" and "ColorfulLedKeyboardService"
  are still recognized by the installer for clean upgrades.

Further modifications by downstream maintainers should be appended below with
a date and a short description of the change.

Third-party components
----------------------
- InsydeDCHU.dll: proprietary keyboard driver shipped by Clevo / Insyde as part
  of the OEM Control Center software. It is NOT distributed with this
  repository and is NOT covered by the GPL-3.0 license of this project. End
  users must obtain it from their OEM-provided Control Center installation.